data.description: This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is nestled at the end of a quiet dead-end street, offering a peaceful and private setting. With its cute and inviting exterior, this home exudes warmth and character.  As you enter, you are greeted by a cozy living room featuring large windows that allow natural light to flood the space. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area, creating a perfect space for entertaining family and friends.  The kitchen is well-appointed with modern appliances, ample cabinet space, providing a functional and stylish space to prepare delicious meals.  The primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom for added privacy. The two additional bedrooms are spacious and bright.  Outside, the backyard is a hidden gem, providing a serene escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. It offers a perfect spot for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing on a sunny day.  Located at the end of a dead-end street, this home offers a sense of seclusion while still being conveniently close to schools, parks, shopping centers, and major transportation routes. It provides the best of both worlds - a peaceful oasis within reach of all the amenities you need.  Don't miss the opportunity to own this adorable 3 bedroom, 2 bath home tucked away in a quiet and desirable location. It is the perfect place to create lasting memories and call home!
